text: Mamadou Sakho is a wrestler from Senegal. Sakho competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics, the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. He was born on 25 January 1951.Mamadou Sakho == References == Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese wrestlers Category:Olympians for Senegal
